snippet.title: AirportSim - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A new experience from the minds at MS Games has been announced at the Future Games Show called AirportSim. The new contemporary simulator will allow you to play the role of an airport ground handler where efficiency, time and precision matter.

Learn more about AirportSim at FSElite.
https://fselite.net/content/experience-the-life-of-a-ground-handler-with-airportsim-by-ms-games/

Or on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1715280/AirportSim/
